import React from 'react';
import styles from './index.module.scss';
import classNames from 'classnames';


export class TravelForm extends React.Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <form action="" className={classNames(styles['travelForm'], 'trabelForm')}>
                <label>
                    名字:
                    <input type="text" name="name" />
                </label>
                <label>
                    电话:
                    <input type="number" name="elephone" />
                </label>
                <label>
                    出发地:
                    <input type="text" name="departure" />
                </label>
                <label>
                    目的地:
                    <input type="text" name="destination" />
                </label>
                <label>
                    旅行时间:
                    <input type="text" name="time" />
                </label>
                <label>
                    旅行人数:
                    <input type="number" name="count" />
                </label>
                <label>
                    老人人数:
                    <input type="number" name="old" />
                </label>
                <label>
                    孩子人数:
                    <input type="number" name="children" />
                </label>
                <label>
                    必玩景区:
                    <input type="text" name="mustScenicSpots" />
                </label>
                <label>
                    备注:
                    <input type="text" name="remarks" />
                </label>
                <input type="submit" value="提交" />
            </form>
        );
    }
}
